searchableProductInfo.editorsNotes: Fashionistas can't wait to see how Proenza Schouler will reinvent its beloved 'PS1' satchel next, and this floral-print canvas and leather version doesn't disappoint. Tapping SS12's vibrant patterns has never been easier - simply carry this Hawaiian-inspired bag with on or off-duty looks for an instant high-style makeover.Shown here with: Proenza Schouler top, Bottega Veneta bracelet, Eddie Borgo bangles, Mason by Michelle Mason skirt, Alexander McQueen shoes.
